                |Hot down the platforms and devices you need to test on;
              li
                |Describe your project shortly;
              li
                |Tune your requirements in real-time;
              li
                |No sign-up needed.

    .page-content-row-wrap.how_it_works-row-wrap
      .row
        .columns.large-3.image-column
          .svg-wrap ng-include="'/assets/rf-icon-main-2.svg'"
        .columns.large-8
          .header
            |Get the team of professional testers
          .time
            |[5-10 minutes]
          .description
