              |After you submit your requirements, we get in touch with you instantly to discuss timelines and manage other details.
            p
              |Based on your request, an experienced, professional, and skilled team of testers will be assigned to your project.

    .page-content-row-wrap.how_it_works-row-wrap
      .row

        .columns.large-3.image-column
          .svg-wrap ng-include="'/assets/rf-icon-main-3.svg'"

        .columns.large-8
          .header
            |Get your results fast
          .time
